                    different sources and getting certified. If you need personal
                    time with a specialist, don’t hesitate to book your slot with
                    one of our top coaches.
                </p>

                <button class="welcomeButton">Explore Courses</button>
                <button id="midRightButton" class="welcomeButton">Find Coaches</button>
            </div>
        </div>

